{"tid":2142837,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"包商銀行嚴重資不抵債，將被申請破產","createTime":"2020-08-06T16:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T18:32:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f968918bfc76253ba022d98f61ead696eef9a017","tid":2142837,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542275-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542275-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOocyEe9XGSmm9RGcz8BbYLg%3D&h=3ef47dc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542275-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=eb0eadf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542275-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n人民銀行表示，根據前期包商銀行嚴重資不抵債的清產核資結果，包商銀行將被申請破產，有關部門正依法依規對相關人員追責問責。<br />\n<br />\n人行發布第2季度貨幣政策執行報告，並以專欄形式首次披露包商銀行處置情況，表示為保障包商銀行流動性安全，接管以來人行在接受足額優質抵押品前提下，向包商銀行提供235億元人民幣額度常備借貸便利流動性支持，不僅高於2004年證券公司綜合治理時期的保障程度，與國際上同類型機構風險處置時的債權保障程度相比，亦是比較高的水平。<br />\n<br />\n貨幣政策執行報告又提到，高風險中小金融機構處置順利實施，積極化解部分城市商業銀行、農村商業銀行、農村信用社多年隱藏的風險，最大程度保護債權人合法權益。推動省級政府「一省一策」制定中小金融機構風險處置規劃。錦州銀行、恒豐銀行改革重組方案順利實施。<br />\n<br />\n人行在5月時提到，因疫情影響，包商銀行後續依法處置工作進度需適當延後，接管期限延長6個月，直至今年11月23日。"},{"pid":"8b7764e4b5add80b9391e1271c196c0230d6b6b7","tid":2142837,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"first blood"},{"pid":"ca248894f4ebec0a0689c010953572cbccbe86fc","tid":2142837,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"幾時到人民銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da03a65b45d77187ef44a0ace06b52fdd35b0b5","tid":2142837,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T17:14:38.000Z","msg":"包傷銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a311139960ae0a6f5626bc3033bfd4741578b642","tid":2142837,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:32:24.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}